《'''罌粟花'''》是[[梵高|梵高]]1887完成的一幅油畫，其價值達5000万到5500万美元。<ref name="chief sleepless">{{cite news |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/idUSTRE67N3WL20100824?loomia_ow=t0:s0:a49:g43:r4:c0.089440:b36791924:z0 |title=Egypt culture chief sleepless over Van Gogh theft |publisher=[[Reuters|Reuters]] |date=2010-08-24 |accessdate=2015-11-14 |archive-date=2021-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210310215835/https://www.reuters.com/article/idUSTRE67N3WL20100824?loomia_ow=t0:s0:a49:g43:r4:c0.089440:b36791924:z0 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 2010年被人從[[開羅|開羅]]的{{Internal link helper/en|默罕默德·艾哈迈迪·哈利勒博物馆|Mohamed Mahmoud Khalil Museum}}盜走，至今尚未尋囘。<ref name="officials jailed" /> 同年10月包括埃及文化部代理部長在内的11人被判玩忽職守，在繳納罰金之後獲釋。<ref name="officials jailed">{{Cite news|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-11529187|title=Egyptian ministry officials jailed over Van Gogh theft|publisher=[[BBC_News|BBC News]]|date=2020-10-12|accessdate=2015-11-14|archive-date=2021-03-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210310215831/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-11529187|dead-url=no}}</ref> 而早在1977年6月4日它就曾被人偷走過一次，10年後才于[[科威特|科威特]]追回。<ref name="still missing">{{Cite news|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-11050207|title=Egyptian minister says Van Gogh picture still missing| publisher=[[BBC_News|BBC News]]|date=2010-08-22|archive-date=2010-08-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100822131901/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-11050207|dead-url=no}}</ref>
這副畫繪製的是插在花瓶中的黃色和紅色的[[罌粟花|罌粟花]]。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.artdaily.org/index.asp?int_sec=11&int_new=46742 |title=Egypt Court Jails Officials Over Van Gogh's "Vase with Viscaria" Stolen in August |publisher=artdaily.org |date=2011-04-22|archive-date=2012-03-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120321213350/http://www.artdaily.org/index.asp?int_sec=11&int_new=46742|dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="stolen in Cairo">{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-11050040|title=Van Gogh painting stolen in Cairo|publisher=[[BBC_News|BBC News]]|date=2010-08-21|accessdate=2015-11-14|archive-date=2021-03-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210310215601/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-11050040|dead-url=no}}</ref> 這幅畫的技巧來自梵高敬仰的法國畫家{{Internal link helper/en|阿道夫·蒙蒂塞利|Adolphe Monticelli}}，1886年梵高曾在巴黎看過他的作品。<ref>[http://www.guardian.co.uk/artanddesign/2010/aug/22/stolen-van-gogh-still-missing Guardian, ''Stolen Van Gogh Still Missing''] {{Wayback|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/artanddesign/2010/aug/22/stolen-van-gogh-still-missing |date=20120420064500 }} Retrieved August 26, 2010</ref>

